ther_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Takazudo/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Takazudo/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Takazudo/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Takazudo/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Takazudo/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Takazudo/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Takazudo/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"labels":[{"id":10789145995,"node_id":"LA_kwDOSMh-vc8AAAACgxVNiw","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/Takazudo/zudo-front-builder/labels/epic","name":"epic","color":"1D76DB","default":false,"description":"Big-plan epic tracking multiple sub-issues or topics"}],"state":"closed","locked":false,"assignees":[],"milestone":null,"comments":5,"created_at":"2026-04-25T20:29:02Z","updated_at":"2026-04-26T07:06:16Z","closed_at":"2026-04-26T07:06:16Z","assignee":null,"author_association":"OWNER","active_lock_reason":null,"sub_issues_summary":{"total":0,"completed":0,"percent_completed":0},"issue_dependencies_summary":{"blocked_by":0,"total_blocked_by":0,"blocking":0,"total_blocking":0},"body":"- https://github.com/Takazudo/zudo-front-builder/issues/2\n\n---\n\n**Super-epic:** #2\n**Super-epic base branch:** `base/zfb-init`\n**This epic's base branch:** `base/zfb-init-dev-server`\n\n## Overview\n\nThe dev-mode HTTP server. Wraps Epic 6's `zfb-build` plus an `axum` server that serves rendered HTML from memory, static assets from disk, and a `/__zfb/reload` SSE endpoint that pushes \"page\" or \"css\" events. A small browser script reloads on \"page\" events and swaps `<link>` href on \"css\" events without full reload.\n\n## Dependencies\n\nEpics 4 + 5 + 6 (the dev server wires them together to serve real output).\n\n## Sub-tasks (6)\n\n1. **`zfb-server` crate** — `crates/zfb-server/`. Depend on `axum`, `tokio`, `tower-http`. Top-level `serve(opts: ServeOpts)` async fn.\n\n2. **HTTP routes** — GET `/` and `/*path` serve rendered HTML from `zfb-build`'s in-memory page cache; GET `/assets/*` serve from `dist/assets/` on disk; GET `/public/*` serve from `public/` (user assets); 404 for unknown paths.\n\n3. **SSE endpoint** — GET `/__zfb/reload` opens an SSE stream; `zfb-build`'s rebuild events push `event: page` or `event: css` lines.\n\n4. **Browser live-reload script** — emit a tiny (~30 LOC) script at `/__zfb/livereload.js`. Connects to the SSE endpoint, listens for `page` (calls `location.reload()`) and `css` (rewrites `<link rel=\"stylesheet\">` href to bust cache).\n\n5. **Inject script into rendered pages** — dev mode only; prod build omits the `<script src=\"/__zfb/livereload.js\">` tag.\n\n6. **Tests** — start the server with a fixture project, change a markdown file, assert the SSE event fires and the page re-renders. Change a CSS file, assert `css` event fires.\n\n## Acceptance criteria\n\n- `cargo run -p zfb-server` (placeholder until Epic 8's CLI lands) starts the dev server on `localhost:3000`.\n- Editing markdown triggers an SSE `page` event; browser reloads; new content visible.\n- Editing CSS triggers `css` event; browser swaps `<link>`; no full reload.\n- HTTP 404 returns the dev-mode 404 page (custom or default).\n\n## Instructions for `/x-wt-teams`\n\n```\n/x-wt-teams https://github.com/Takazudo/zudo-front-builder/issues/8\n```\n\nCreates `base/zfb-init-dev-server` off `base/zfb-init`. Epic-PR merges into the super-epic base.\n","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/Takazudo/zudo-front-builder/issues/8/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/Takazudo/zudo-front-builder/issues/8/timeline","performed_via_github_app":null,"state_reason":"completed","pinned_comment":null,"score":1.0},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/tokio-rs/axum/issues/1952","reposito